strings: <voice_0x01001622><se_def>*: A fool in waiting! My poor attempts to quit failed!
<voice_0x01001623><se_def>*: Listen, I am the Dark Lord's wanderer! Body regeneration is a long and difficult process.
<voice_0x01001624><se_def>Exploding spikes: How many problems have you come across during this time? But you know it Thank you!
<voice_0x01001625><se_def>Exploding spikes: Since then, the worlds of light and darkness have come together! This alliance is about to start a new government!
<voice_0x01001626><se_def>Exploding spikes: The supreme power rules everything! Dark Lord, Quirrell!
<voice_0x01001627><se_def>Exploding spikes: You are happy with me even with a miserable life!
